_sText:
I've fixed some minor bugs and annoying things in this map. This was done for .Bad deathrun server, so players can enjoy the map more.

I do not own this map. Rate and comment if you want.

-The CT and T spawn was fixed ( no more pressing the button for start )

-CT bug abuse to bypass half of the map was fixed

-The CT to T teleport was fixed, the teleport destination is now higher so the T's can't backstab CT's.

Enjoy! :)
